DataHandler should serve for several purposes:
    1. provide utilities to use with XML
        _parsing XML to object
        _store file location for frequently used

    2. provide model objects to use throughout the project

    3. provide utilities to use with JSON


The test package include tools to demonstrate how to use the classes
    test.java demonstrate the following
    _how to use queries
    _how to use SAX_Generic_Handler
    _how to get LongBox<GenericObject> from test_LongBex_Object
    _how to use the XMLDatabase which include :
        _create XMLDatabase
        _populate the XMLDatabase content
        _retrieve object (incomplete)
        _add object (incomplete)
        _remove object (incomplete)
        _modify object (incomplete)
